{"tid":1736912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"消防員你地唔配我地叫手足","createTime":"2019-11-18T22:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:41:23.000Z","uid":193541,"like":15,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aae1ee414322e2d3e54dee19f5c6a313397e5a19","tid":1736912,"uid":193541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:46:27.000Z","msg":"分化都咁話<br />\n齊上齊落先係手足<br />\n請問你地做過啲咩<br />\n比曱甴撚 比曱甴點<br />\n都冇反抗嘅想法<br />\n又唔講得立場<br />\n喂公義都唔講得你甘心？<br />\n咪表態唔聽佢點囉<br />\n咩都唔得你地同班&quot;我都只係打份工啫&quot;嘅撚屌有咩分別？<br />\n如果比我講兩句你地又話&quot;好割席吖嘛！咁我地一於企曱甴嗰邊囉！&quot;<br />\n咁我想問<br />\n你而家咪企曱甴嗰邊囉。"},{"pid":"9025e71e9cd18673020955a3ed535463de6eaaac","tid":1736912,"uid":227929,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:47:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>現在嘅時間係06:47 </strong></span></span><br />\n是日方向為割消防<br />\n<br />\nbtw咁早都唔收工?"},{"pid":"e56d20457eb1b6ba68e28b631dace71a2aa3b451","tid":1736912,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9025e71e9cd18673020955a3ed535463de6eaaac","tid":1736912,"uid":227929,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:47:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>現在嘅時間係06:47 </strong></span></span><br />\n是日方向為割消防<br />\n<br />\nbtw咁早都唔收工?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:48:15.000Z","msg":"風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73dc5668b003ce3c0ed4588868e5cf89d6be24c4","tid":1736912,"uid":193541,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9025e71e9cd18673020955a3ed535463de6eaaac","tid":1736912,"uid":227929,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:47:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>現在嘅時間係06:47 </strong></span></span><br />\n是日方向為割消防<br />\n<br />\nbtw咁早都唔收工?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:53:20.000Z","msg":"on9打完完全瞓唔到<b